'''2013年巴西抗议运动'''（又名'''沙拉反抗'''、'''巴西之秋'''、'''热带之春'''<ref name=" fish" >{{cite web |url=http://finance.qq.com/a/20130620/015953.htm |title=“热带之春”抗议潮震撼巴西 |accessdate=2013年6月21日 |publisher=腾讯网 |work= |language=zh-cn |archive-date=2021年1月8日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108010426/https://finance.qq.com/a/20130620/015953.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是2013年5月爆发在[[巴西|巴西]]几个城市的抗议运动，抗议群体倡导“自由的公共交通”，最初抗议者抗议在巴西几个城市抗议“巴西当局增加[[公共汽车|公共汽车]]、[[火车|火车]]和[[地铁|地铁]]票价”，后来巴西警察用[[暴力|暴力]]镇压抗议者，导致矛盾激化，<ref name=ELPAIS1>{{cite web|last=Arias|first=Juan|title=Brasil se levanta en protesta contra el aumento de los precios del transporte|url=http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2013/06/12/actualidad/1371000636_370579.html|publisher=[[El_País|El País]]|accessdate=13 June 2013|language=es|date=June 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625211047/http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2013/06/12/actualidad/1371000636_370579.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ELPAIS2>{{cite web|last=Arias|first=Juan|title=São Paulo vive una nueva noche de protestas con escenas de guerra|url=http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2013/06/14/actualidad/1371171229_461963.html|publisher=[[El_País|El País]]|accessdate=14 June 2013|language=es|date=14 June 2013|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202105355/http://internacional.elpais.com/internacional/2013/06/14/actualidad/1371171229_461963.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=LEMONDE>{{cite web|last=Arias|first=Juan|title=Brésil : manifestations contre la hausse du prix des transports|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/ameriques/article/2013/06/14/bresil-manifestations-contre-la-hausse-du-prix-des-transports_3430069_3222.html|publisher=[[Le_Monde|Le Monde]]|accessdate=14 June 2013|language=fr|date=14 June 2013|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809022333/http://www.lemonde.fr/ameriques/article/2013/06/14/bresil-manifestations-contre-la-hausse-du-prix-des-transports_3430069_3222.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CNN>{{cite web|last=Brocchetto|first=Marilia|title=Protesters, police clash in Sao Paulo streets over fare increases|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/06/12/world/americas/brazil-protests/index.html|publisher=CNN|accessdate=13 June 2013|date=12 June 2013|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182249/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/06/12/world/americas/brazil-protests/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月中旬，抗议运动扩大，是巴西自1992年抗议[[巴西总统|总统]][[费尔南多·科洛尔·德梅洛|费尔南多·科洛尔·德梅洛]]当局以来最大的抗议运动。<ref name="anistia"/><ref name=GDP>{{cite web |url=http://www.gazetadopovo.com.br/vidaecidadania/conteudo.phtml?tl=1&id=1381932&tit=Associacao-de-jornais-condena-acao-da-PM |title=Associação de jornais condena ação da PM |publisher=Gazeta do Povo |date=2013-06-14 |accessdate=2013-06-20 |language=pt |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407083148/http://www.gazetadopovo.com.br/vidaecidadania/conteudo.phtml?tl=1&id=1381932&tit=Associacao-de-jornais-condena-acao-da-PM |archive-date=2014-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此次抗议运动中，新闻媒体和社交媒体在抗议运动中扮演了抗议者彼此之间联系和为公共事业大声疾呼的作用。<ref name="el país"/><ref name="social media">{{cite web|title=SP: página no Facebook orienta manifestantes para protesto|url=http://noticias.terra.com.br/brasil/cidades/sp-pagina-no-facebook-orienta-manifestantes-para-protesto,be33f8c0f3d4f310VgnVCM3000009acceb0aRCRD.html|language=pt|accessdate=2013-06-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043544/http://noticias.terra.com.br/brasil/cidades/sp-pagina-no-facebook-orienta-manifestantes-para-protesto,be33f8c0f3d4f310VgnVCM3000009acceb0aRCRD.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 名称 ==
巴西政府对抗议当局的事件或运动一般定性词语是“[[叛乱|叛乱]]”。<ref name="vinagre">{{cite web |url=http://colunas.revistagalileu.globo.com/buzz/2013/06/14/como-o-vinagre-virou-simbolo-da-revolta-da-salada/ |title=How vinegar became a symbol of the "Salad Rebellion" |editor=Galileu (magazine) |date=14 June 2013 |accessdate=14 June 2013 |language=pt |archive-date=2013-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619214909/http://colunas.revistagalileu.globo.com/buzz/2013/06/14/como-o-vinagre-virou-simbolo-da-revolta-da-salada/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=g1>{{cite web|url=http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2013/06/presos-em-protestos-em-sp-relatam-detencoes-por-spray-e-vinagre.html|title=Arrested São Paulo protesters claim detentions based on acts of spraying and because they carried vinegar|author=Rodrigo Mora|publisher=G1|date=13 June  2013|language=pt|accessdate=2013-06-21|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114023455/http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2013/06/presos-em-protestos-em-sp-relatam-detencoes-por-spray-e-vinagre.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cartacapital>{{cite web|url=http://www.cartacapital.com.br/politica/em-sao-paulo-vinagre-da-cadeia-4469.html|title=In São Paulo, vinegar is a criminal act|date=13 June 2013|author=Piero Locatelli|language=pt|accessdate=2013-06-21|archive-date=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701032855/http://www.cartacapital.com.br/politica/em-sao-paulo-vinagre-da-cadeia-4469.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>20世纪初，该名字最初出现在[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]，后来，以类似的方式的抗议活动在[[圣保罗_(巴西)|圣保罗]]出现，超过60个抗议者被逮捕，他们因为携带[[醋|醋]]作为一种保护反对警察使用[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]和[[胡椒|胡椒]]喷雾。<ref>{{pt}}[http://noticias.uol.com.br/cotidiano/ultimas-noticias/2013/06/13/jornalista-e-preso-durante-protesto-contra-aumento-da-tarifa-em-sp.htm Journalist arrested for carrying vinegar in demonstration against fare hiking is liberated] {{Wayback|url=http://noticias.uol.com.br/cotidiano/ultimas-noticias/2013/06/13/jornalista-e-preso-durante-protesto-contra-aumento-da-tarifa-em-sp.htm |date=20210114023459 }}</ref><ref name="youpix1">{{cite web|url=http://youpix.com.br/viral-2/a-marcha-do-vinagre-ja-e-o-mais-novo-movimento-revolucionario-da-internet/|title=Vinegar March is the newest revolutionary movement of the internet|publisher=YouPIX|date=14 June 2013|author=Bia Bonduki|accessdate=15 June 2013|language=pt|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618040533/http://youpix.com.br/viral-2/a-marcha-do-vinagre-ja-e-o-mais-novo-movimento-revolucionario-da-internet/|archivedate=2013年6月18日}}</ref>

另一个流行的名字是“巴西之秋”，来源于[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]事件。另外，“热带之春”也被媒体广发引用。<ref>{{pt}} [http://arquivo.dm.com.br/texto/gz/121469 Youth rebellion in Brazil's autumn] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130624143327/http://arquivo.dm.com.br/texto/gz/121469 |date=2013-06-24 }}</ref><ref>{{pt}} [http://blogs.lancenet.com.br/maurobeting/2013/06/15/outono-brasileiro/ Brazilian Autumn] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.lancenet.com.br/maurobeting/2013/06/15/outono-brasileiro/ |date=20131203001832 }}</ref> <ref>{{pt}} [http://www.cartacapital.com.br/politica/a-primavera-brasileira/ the Brazilian Spring] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cartacapital.com.br/politica/a-primavera-brasileira/ |date=20210114023535 }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
2012年8月9月，第一次抗议运动发生在[[北里奥格兰德|北里奥格兰德]][[纳塔尔|纳塔尔]]，巴西当局称之为“叛乱”，抗议者的目的和诉求是当地市政厅减少车费价格。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tribunadonorte.com.br/noticia/cmn-revoga-reajuste-das-passagens-de-onibus/230884 |title=CMN revoga reajuste das passagens de ônibus |publisher=Tribuna do Norte |date=2012-09-06 |accessdate=2013-06-20 |language=pt |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114023525/http://www.tribunadonorte.com.br/noticia/cmn-revoga-reajuste-das-passagens-de-onibus/230884 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年3月，类似的抗议活动在[[阿雷格里港|阿雷格里港]]爆发，抗议者的行动促使当地市政厅减少车费价格。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zerohora.clicrbs.com.br/rs/noticia/2013/06/vandalismo-marcou-protesto-em-porto-alegre-contra-a-tarifa-de-onibus-4169886.html|title=Vandalismo marcou protesto em Porto Alegre contra a tarifa de ônibus|publisher=[[Zero_Hora|Zero Hora]]|date=14 June 2013|accessdate=14 June 2013|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029213641/http://zerohora.clicrbs.com.br/rs/noticia/2013/06/vandalismo-marcou-protesto-em-porto-alegre-contra-a-tarifa-de-onibus-4169886.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[哥亚尼亚|哥亚尼亚]]，抗议运动开始于5月16日，5月28日，当地抗议运动达到顶峰。<ref name=DMG>{{Cite web |url=http://arquivo.dm.com.br/texto/gz/120788 |title=Diário da Manhã: Passagem de ônibus voltou a custar R$ 2,70 |accessdate=2013-06-21 |archive-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130616054147/http://arquivo.dm.com.br/texto/gz/120788 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在比比拉广场，公交车被毁，2人被焚烧和2人被石头打死。<ref name=DMG/>24名学生因为“破坏公物和叛乱罪”被捕。<ref name=DMG/>另一次示威发生在6月6日，当学生在市中心街道放火烧车[[轮胎|轮胎]]、投掷自制[[炸弹|炸弹]]、打破警车的窗户。6月13日，公交车票价回退，但是巴西公民并没有获益。<ref name=DMG/>

在[[圣保罗_(巴西)|圣保罗]]，抗议运动始于当地市政厅和圣保罗州政府宣布提高公交车票价，从3.00[[巴西雷亚尔|巴西雷亚尔]]上升到3.20巴西雷亚尔。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite web |url=http://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/noticia/2013-06-11/manifestantes-contra-aumento-da-passagem-entram-em-conflito-com-pm-em-sao-paulo |title=Agência Brasil: Manifestantes contra aumento da passagem entram em conflito com PM em São Paulo |accessdate=2013-06-21 |archive-date=2013-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131121141400/http://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/noticia/2013-06-11/manifestantes-contra-aumento-da-passagem-entram-em-conflito-com-pm-em-sao-paulo |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2011年1月，也有过类似的抗议运动。<ref name=tarifakassab>{{cite web|last=|first=|title=Tarifa de ônibus em São Paulo sobe para R$ 3|url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/cotidiano/855066-tarifa-de-onibus-em-sao-paulo-sobe-para-r-3.shtml|publisher=[[Folha_de_S.Paulo|Folha de S.Paulo]]|accessdate=13 June 2013|language=pt|date=2011-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108010816/https://www1.folha.uol.com.br/cotidiano/855066-tarifa-de-onibus-em-sao-paulo-sobe-para-r-3.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2012年2月，火车和地铁票价已经提高到相同的价格。<ref>{{cite web|last=Magalhães|first=Vera|coauthor=Lima, Daniela|title=Grupo invade Alesp para protestar contra Kassab e aumento do ônibus|url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/poder/891749-grupo-invade-alesp-para-protestar-contra-kassab-e-aumento-do-onibus.shtml|publisher=[[Folha_de_S.Paulo|Folha de S.Paulo]]|accessdate=13 June 2013|language=pt|date=2011-03-21|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108010703/https://www1.folha.uol.com.br/poder/891749-grupo-invade-alesp-para-protestar-contra-kassab-e-aumento-do-onibus.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年，新市长[[费尔南多·哈达德|费尔南多·哈达德]]宣布票价将提高。<ref name="metro3">{{cite web|url=http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2012/02/valor-da-tarifa-de-trem-e-do-metro-de-sp-sobe-para-r-3-neste-domingo.html|title=Valor da tarifa de trem e do Metrô de SP sobe para R$ 3 neste domingo|date=12 de fevereiro de 2012|publisher=Portal G1|language=pt|accessdate=14 June 2013|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108010710/http://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/2012/02/valor-da-tarifa-de-trem-e-do-metro-de-sp-sobe-para-r-3-neste-domingo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月，联邦政府宣布公共交通将免于支付2个税务，试图抑制通货膨胀。<ref name=novahaddad>{{cite web|last=|first=|coauthor=Lima, Daniela|title=São Paulo terá nova tarifa de ônibus no 1º semestre, diz Haddad|url=http://noticias.uol.com.br/ultimas-noticias/agencia-estado/2013/01/14/sp-tera-nova-tarifa-de-onibus-no-1-semestre-diz-haddad.htm|publisher=[[Folha_de_S.Paulo|Folha de S.Paulo]]|accessdate=13 June 2013|language=pt|date=14 January 2013|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114023531/https://noticias.uol.com.br/ultimas-noticias/agencia-estado/2013/01/14/sp-tera-nova-tarifa-de-onibus-no-1-semestre-diz-haddad.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管如此，票价从3.00巴西雷亚尔提高到3.20巴西雷亚尔，6月2日爆发了大规模的抗议运动。<ref name="MP">{{cite web|url=http://ultimosegundo.ig.com.br/brasil/2013-05-23/governo-confirma-mp-para-diminuir-impostos-do-transporte-publico.html|title=Governo confirma MP para diminuir impostos do transporte público|date=23 de maio de 2013|publisher=[[Internet_Group|Portal IG]]|language=pt|accessdate=14 June 2013|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005120408/http://ultimosegundo.ig.com.br/brasil/2013-05-23/governo-confirma-mp-para-diminuir-impostos-do-transporte-publico.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

